Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/dmayle/dm-dotfiles.git ~/.dm-dotfiles

Create symlinks:

    ln -s .dm-dotfiles/vim ~/.vim
    ln -s .dm-dotfiles/bash/bashrc ~/.bashrc
    ln -s .dm-dotfiles/screen/screenrc ~/.screenrc
    ln -s .vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.dm-dotfiles
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
